infoLinks.content:
The new Southern footbridge, Marian Street concourse and Little Eveleigh Street concourse at Redfern Station are now open.  Six new lifts have been installed for customers traveling to and from Redfern Platforms 1 to 10. Barrier-free community access is available for members of the public wishing to cross from one side of the station to the other side.
Please follow signs and see station staff if you need assistance.
